arm_strategy: I looked for some specific traits when I choose most recognizable ones. For example fingerlike drawings are strong indications of an arm and also a v like things reminds me arm which looks like bent arm. Then I choose least recognizable ones. They are generally very abstract drawings. I can think them as arms but I can also think them as really different things. If I have to come up with a methodology it would be first think the all possibilities comes to your mind. If the number of possibilities are few and not very distinct then an arm then it is more recognizable. Otherwise, if I can resemble the image different distinct objects and their number is high it is less recognizable.
